00229 // Note(agnat): When passing overloaded function pointers to template functions
00230 // as generic arguments the compiler needs help in picking the right overload.
00231 // These two functions handle New<Function> and New<FunctionTemplate> with
00232 // all argument variations.
00233 
00234 // v8::Function and v8::FunctionTemplate with one or two arguments
00235 template <typename T>
00236 typename imp::Factory<T>::return_t
00237 New( FunctionCallback callback
00238       , v8::Local<v8::Value> data = v8::Local<v8::Value>()) {
00239     return imp::Factory<T>::New(callback, data);
00240 }
00241 
00242 // v8::Function and v8::FunctionTemplate with three arguments
00243 template <typename T, typename A2>
00244 typename imp::Factory<T>::return_t
00245 New( FunctionCallback callback
00246       , v8::Local<v8::Value> data = v8::Local<v8::Value>()
00247       , A2 a2 = A2()) {
00248     return imp::Factory<T>::New(callback, data, a2);
